  "title": "Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking energetic and dynamic personnel to join our team.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Delivery of beverages to homes/offices/assigned outlets. (islandwide)</li>\n  <li>Loading and unloading of goods onto vehicle according to delivery order (able to lift heavy items)</li>\n  <li>Delivering goods to our customers in a professional, courteous, and timely manner</li>\n  <li>Compliance to internal standard operating procedures during delivery</li>\n  <li>Assist in ad-hoc duties when necessary</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and in team</li>\n  <li>Possess valid Singapore Class 3 driving license and good record with no traffic offence</li>\n  <li>Min 2 years experience in driving</li>\n  <li>Prior delivery experience and good road knowledge will be preferred</li>\n  <li>5/6 days work week</li>\n</ul>",
